video.title: The L.A. Complex
video.synopsis: A group of twenty-something performers living in the same Los Angeles apartment complex pursue their dreams of Hollywood success.

episodes.synopsis: Broke and desperate, aspiring actress Abby finds a place to crash at the Lux Motel in L.A. Here, she meets a group of like-minded displaced dreamers.
episodes.title: Down In L.A

episodes.synopsis: Abby is given the chance to make some big money. Raquel decides she's not going to wait by the phone any longer and starts pushing to get a film made.
episodes.title: Do Something

episodes.synopsis: After her Hollywood stock has plummeted, Raquel is dumped by her agency. Offended and angry, she's even more hell-bent on getting her script optioned.
episodes.title: Who You Know

episodes.synopsis: Tariq and Kal take a break from L.A. to relax and develop a new layer to their friendship. Raquel looks to Gary and Connor to make her feel better.
episodes.title: Other Side Of The Door

episodes.synopsis: Raquel should be ecstatic after finally securing financing for her project but finds herself questioning her methods of making it happen.
episodes.title: Home

episodes.synopsis: Nick and Abby are trying to move past the casual phase of their relationship while still desperately trying to make their career dreams come true.
episodes.title: Burn It Down

episodes.synopsis: Kal's legal team offers Tariq money in exchange for his silence. Tariq turns down Kal's money and tells him he never wants to see him again.
episodes.title: Vacancy

episodes.synopsis: Abby books a role on "Saving Grace," a conservative Christian TV show. She accidentally walks in on the show's stars having sex.
episodes.title: The Contract

episodes.synopsis: Kal's team encourages him to do a press tour for his upcoming record. During a radio interview, Kal recognizes a mysterious caller's voice.
episodes.title: Choose Your Battles

episodes.synopsis: In need of a place to stay after breaking up with Nick, Abby accepts Brandon's offer to stay at the apartment he shares with Laura.
episodes.title: Be A Man

episodes.synopsis: Raquel calls Connor after she is arrested for a DUI, but bristles when Connor's fake girlfriend accompanies Connor to bail Raquel out of jail.
episodes.title: Taking The Day

episodes.synopsis: Abby moves into the Lux after her relationship with Brandon and Laura grows complicated. Laura discovers Abby and Brandon cheating behind her back.
episodes.title: Rules Of Thirds

episodes.synopsis: Kaldrick and Dawna begin sleeping together. Infinite Jest and his lawyer threaten to sue Kal for Rook assaulting Infinite at Kal's party.
episodes.title: Half Way

episodes.synopsis: Connor is caught off guard when Jennifer ends their fake relationship to reconcile with her estranged husband. Kevin and Cam help Beth look for Simon.
episodes.title: Stay

episodes.synopsis: Connor is surprised by the sudden arrival of his long-lost sister. Raquel is dropped by her agent and is forced to declare bankruptcy.
episodes.title: Help Wanted

episodes.synopsis: Kal and Abby set off together to find Tariq. Connor's sister introduces him to an interesting new religion. Beth and Simon get a surprise visitor.
episodes.title: Make It Right

episodes.synopsis: Kal is beginning to feel good again when a phone call rocks his world. Raquel continues to do whatever it takes to make money to finance her film.
episodes.title: Now Or Never

episodes.synopsis: Abby panics after making a very impulsive move with Gray. Kal struggles to make a decision about his relationship with his dad.
episodes.title: X's And O's

episodes.synopsis: Horrified by an uncomfortable moment with Charlotte, Connor seeks solace in Scienetics. Raquel prepares for a fundraiser.
episodes.title: Don't Say Goodbye
